<Body><Title>俄称制止针对索契奥运设施恐怖袭击 未透露细节</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2014年4月11日</ReportTime>
	<Content><Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s1">中国网</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">4月11日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">讯</Denoter></Event>
 据俄新网消息，<Event eid="e2" type="thoughtevent">俄联邦安全局局长<Participant sid="s2">博尔特尼科夫</Participant><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">周四（4月10日）</Time><Denoter did="d2" type="statement">表示</Denoter></Event>，
 <Event eid="e3"><Participant sid="s3">俄安全局和一些列其它国家</Participant><Denoter did="d3" type="operation">制止</Denoter>了针对<Object oid="o3">索契奥运设施</Object>实施的<Object oid="o3">恐怖袭击</Object>，</Event>包括
 <Event eid="e4">使用<Means mid="m4" type="tool">自杀式炸弹</Means><Denoter did="d4" type="emergency">爆炸</Denoter>。</Event></Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e5" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s5,s6">博尔特尼科夫</Participant><Denoter did="d5" type="statement">表示</Denoter></Event>，
正因为<Event eid="e6" type="thoughtevent"><Denoter did="d6" type="perception">担心</Denoter></Event>
				<Event eid="e7"><Time tid="t7" type="timeInterval">冬奥会期间</Time>会对<Denoter did="d7" type="movement">飞往</Denoter><Location lid="l7" type="destination">索契</Location><Object oid="o7,o8">航班</Object></Event>
				<Event eid="e8">实施<Denoter did="d8" type="emergency">恐怖袭击</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e9" polarity="negative">所有才不允许<Denoter did="d9" type="action">携带</Denoter><Object oid="o9">液体</Object>。</Event></Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e10" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s10">他</Participant><Denoter did="d10" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，“
一切都是有根据和计划的，<Event eid="e11">因为<Participant sid="s11">恐怖分子</Participant><Denoter did="d11" type="action">使用</Denoter>过或者想使用引爆炸药的媒介之一，正是<Object oid="o11">特别液体</Object>”。</Event></Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e12" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s12">博尔特尼科夫</Participant><Time tid="t12" type="relTime">昨日</Time><Denoter did="d12" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>
				<Event eid="e13"><Denoter did="d13" type="action">制止</Denoter>了索契的<Object oid="o13">恐怖袭击</Object></Event>，但
<Event eid="e14" polarity="negative">没有<Denoter did="d14" type="statement">明确</Denoter>行动的<Object oid="o14">具体细节</Object>。</Event></Sentence></Paragraph></Content>

